name: transdecoder

owner.description: Bioconda is a distribution of bioinformatics software realized as a channel for the versatile Conda package manager.
owner.name: bioconda

summary: TransDecoder identifies candidate coding regions within transcript sequences, such as those generated by de novo RNA-Seq transcript assembly using Trinity, or constructed based on RNA-Seq alignments to the genome using Tophat and Cufflinks.
